      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle that offers an affordable path to ownership. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a practical option for local driving, a first-time buyer, or someone needing dependable basic transportation without a big investment. Priced to move and presented as an honest value opportunity.",
