      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly ride for someone who wants affordable wheels without a lot of fuss. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it starts, runs, and can be a great option for a commuter, first-time driver, or anyone needing basic transportation. Priced fairly for what it is, and represented honestly by a seller who believes in being upfront. If you want dependable-enough transportation at a sensible price, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for someone who knows their way around a toolbox. This car is a usable project with a strong mechanical foundation, offering a complete drivetrain, responsive steering feel, and the kind of analog driving character enthusiasts look for. It shows age and will need cosmetic and general reconditioning, but it presents as an honest platform for a budget build, commuter revival, or parts-supported restoration. A good candidate for someone wanting a capable chassis at an accessible entry point without paying premium-market money.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Rough around the edges, but it gets the job done. Cheap entry car or solid project. Priced to sell fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car for someone who sees possibility where others see patina. It has a road-worn presence and an honest, unmistakable character that gives it more soul than many newer machines. Whether you want an affordable project, a dependable around-town runabout with personality, or a platform to make your own, this one offers a lot of story for the money. It\u2019s not pretending to be perfect\u2014it\u2019s a car with grit, presence, and plenty of life left for the right owner.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
